name: ArgonLabs Shatterglassbomb
description:
A Tribute to AlexDelia's Artifact Quest!
Icosphere shatterglass, a cube of pure toxic diesel and a lava fuse.

This all combines into a powerfull weapon against biological beings.
Upon explosion, thousands of shards fly of, injuring anything in range.
Get some before Scramblercity goes down not only to skreeds but also to weird mutant beings.

! Handle with care, fuse is allways live !
